  "id": "BIT-discourse-2026-33394",
  "summary": "Discourse leaks PM post edits to moderators",
  "details": "Discourse is an open-source discussion platform. Prior to versions 2026.3.0, 2026.2.1, and 2026.1.2, the Post Edits admin report (/admin/reports/post_edits) leaked the first 40 characters of raw post content from private messages and secure categories to moderators who shouldn't have access. Versions 2026.3.0, 2026.2.1, and 2026.1.2 contain a patch. No known workarounds are available.",
